10:T595,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"One-Punch Man Season 3","description":"The third season of <i>One Punch Man</i>.<br><br>\nSaitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of \"special training,\" he’s become so strong that he's practically invincible. In fact, he's too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association.<br><br>\nOne day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a \"human monster\" who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout.<br><br>\n(Source: EMOTION Label YouTube Channel Description)<br><br>\n<i>Note: Excludes recap episode that aired a week before regular broadcast.</i>","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx153800-8SpzdHOaZCoU.jpg","datePublished":"2025-10-12","numberOfEpisodes":12,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["Action","Comedy","Sci-Fi","Supernatural"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":5,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"7904fe40-cefe-4908-b3ec-af6193556912","tmdb_id":153800,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"One-Punch Man Season 3","original_title":"ワンパンマン３","overview":"The third season of <i>One Punch Man</i>.<br><br>\nSaitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of \"special training,\" he’s become so strong that he's practically invincible. In fact, he's too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association.<br><br>\nOne day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a \"human monster\" who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout.<br><br>\n(Source: EMOTION Label YouTube Channel Description)<br><br>\n<i>Note: Excludes recap episode that aired a week before regular broadcast.</i>","poster_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx153800-8SpzdHOaZCoU.jpg","backdrop_path":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/153800-bgkLxE9SHmUi.jpg","release_date":null,"first_air_date":"2025-10-12","status":"published","original_language":"ja","origin_country":["JP"],"genres":[{"id":1,"name":"Action"},{"id":2,"name":"Comedy"},{"id":3,"name":"Sci-Fi"},{"id":4,"name":"Supernatural"}],"popularity":135124,"vote_average":5,"vote_count":null,"runtime":24,"number_of_seasons":null,"number_of_episodes":12,"created_at":"2026-05-02T08:49:36.943447+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-02T08:49:36.899+00:00","tagline":null,"homepage":null,"budget":null,"revenue":null,"production_companies":[{"name":"J.C.STAFF"}],"production_countries":null,"spoken_languages":null,"networks":[],"last_air_date":"2025-12-28","in_production":false,"tmdb_status":"Ended","content_rating":null,"keywords":[{"id":1,"name":"Surreal Comedy"},{"id":2,"name":"Superhero"},{"id":3,"name":"Super Power"},{"id":4,"name":"Parody"},{"id":5,"name":"Male Protagonist"},{"id":6,"name":"Drugs"},{"id":7,"name":"Urban Fantasy"},{"id":8,"name":"Seinen"},{"id":9,"name":"Satire"},{"id":10,"name":"Primarily Adult Cast"},{"id":11,"name":"Primarily Male Cast"},{"id":12,"name":"Urban"},{"id":13,"name":